---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const pageTitle = "About Taksh";
---

<BaseLayout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
	<div
		class="h-screen grid grid-cols-2 overflow-hidden max-h-screen about-wrapper"
	>
		<div class="about-images">
			<div class="flex flex-col h-full">
				<div class="flex-1 border-b border-zinc-950">
					<div class="flex w-full h-full">
						<div class="flex-1 border-r border-zinc-950">
							<img
								src="/nature.jpg"
								alt="nature"
								class="w-full h-full object-cover"
							/>
						</div>
						<div class="flex-1"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="flex-1">
					<div class="flex w-full h-full">
						<div class="flex-1 border-r border-zinc-950"></div>
						<div class="flex-1">
							<img
								src="/me.jpg"
								alt="me"
								class="w-full h-full object-cover"
							/>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div
			class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 h-full w-px bg-zinc-950 center-divider"
		>
		</div>

		<div
			class="flex flex-col justify-start items-start mt-35 ms-30 tracking-wider about-text text-xs opacity-80 relative"
		>
			<span class="txt_bg_clr text-4xl">よ。</span>
			<span class="mt-8">Hi. Thanks for stopping by.</span>
			<span class="mt-2"
				>I'm Taksh Gadhiya, an introvert operating out from <a href="/india" class="tag_button" target="_blank">India</a>.</span
			>
			<span class="mt-2"
				><span class="font-bold">What I do for a living:</span> I write code.</span
			>
			<span class="mt-2"
				><span class="font-bold">What I actually do:</span> I google and copy
				paste things.</span
			>
			<span class="mt-2">I have a shorter stature and normal pores.</span>
			<span class="mt-2">I live quite a low-key life.</span>
			<span class="mt-2"
				><span class="font-bold">Places to visit before I die:</span> Tibet
				& Vietnam.</span
			>
			<span class="mt-2"
				><span class="font-bold">One of my embarrassing habits:</span> Talking
				to myself.</span
			>
			<span class="mt-2"
				>I’m usually quiet online to save excitement for in person
				meetings.</span
			>
			<span class="mt-2"
				>Sometimes it works but most times, I’m seen as a <a class="tag_button"
					href="https://www.hindwi.org/hindi-dictionary/meaning-of-leta-latiif"
					target="_blank"><em>Let Latiif</em></a
				>.</span
			>
			<span class="mt-2 font-bold">You'll probably never see me: </span>
			<div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-2">
				<div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-1">
					<span style="font-size: 20px; color: #000000;">•</span> get angry
				</div>
				<div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-1">
					<span style="font-size: 20px; color: #000000;">•</span> cry
				</div>
				<div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-1">
					<span style="font-size: 20px; color: #000000;">•</span> take photos
					of myself
				</div>
				<div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-1">
					<span style="font-size: 20px; color: #000000;">•</span> follow
					internet trends
				</div>
			</div>
			<span class="mt-2 font-bold">About this website:</span>
			<div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-1">
				<span style="font-size: 20px; color: #000000;">•</span> It has countless
				bugs and unoptimized parts I don't bother to fix.
			</div>
			<div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-1">
				<span style="font-size: 20px; color: #000000;">•</span> You won’t
				find life lessons here. No motivation. No polish. Just lo-fi, trivial,
				occasionally quirky writing.
			</div>
			<span class="mt-8"
				>2025. Made with <a
					href="https://astro.build/"
					target="_blank"
					class="txt_bg_clr">Astro</a
				>.</span
			>
			<div class="flex justify-center items-center">
				<img
					src="/butterfly_flat.avif"
					alt="butterfly flat"
					class="w-full h-full object-cover"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
<style>
	.about-wrapper {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		height: 100vh;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	@media (max-width: 639px) {
		.about-wrapper {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			height: auto;
			min-height: 100vh;
			overflow-y: auto;
			overflow-x: hidden;
		}

		.about-text {
			order: 1;
			margin: 2rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.about-images {
			order: 2;
		}

		.center-divider {
			display: none;
		}
	}
</style>
